Thunder_Kick.help: You perform a strong Thunder Kick which causes smashing damage and hits so hard it might briefly stun your target.
Thunder_Kick.shortHelp: Melee, Minor DMG(Smashing), Chance for Stun(Foe)

Storm_Kick.help: You unleash a roundhouse kick that pummels your foe, causing smashing damage and potentially knocking your target down.
Storm_Kick.shortHelp: Melee, Moderate DMG(Smashing), Chance for Knockdown

Crippling_Axe_Kick.help: You perform a crippling kick which causes smashing damage, immobilizes the target and reduces their movement speed. If the target is flying, they are also brought to the ground.
Crippling_Axe_Kick.targetHelp: You are immobilized an unable to fly. Your movement speeds have been reduced.

High_Pain_Tolerance.help: You have a greater tolerance to pain than others. You are also slightly resistant to all types of damage. This power is always on and costs no Endurance.

Mind_Over_Body.help: Your mind exerts exquisite control over your body, granting you additional resistance to smashing, lethal and psionic damage.

Fast_Healing.help: You regenerate health faster than the average person and are more resistant to regeneration debuffs.

Quick_Recovery.help: You recover endurance faster than the average person.

Heightened_Senses.help: You are more aware of your environment and its hazards. This increases your defense against all typed damage except psionic, improves your perception and makes you more resistant to defense debuffs.
Heightened_Senses.shortHelp: Self (Auto), +DEF(Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Energy, Negative Energy), +RES(-DEF), +Perception
